title: If you can improvise in 12-edo, just build from there.
pid: f86d80fa-d9c4-4b32-894d-051577625069
body: |2-
  Microtonal playing isn't a skill entirely distinct and apart
  from playing ordinary instruments the ordinary way.
  Unless you pick a really weird EDO, most of the music you know
  can probably be translated into your new, higher EDO pretty well.
